  "3207060": {
    "name": "Storefront Simulator Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3207060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras/895fb6a4d5042e681e3eae0d91d317f1.avif?t=1746369392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras_big/895fb6a4d5042e681e3eae0d91d317f1.avif?t=1746369392 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到你自己的商店！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是你的创业故事：从零开始，依靠最基础的店铺，通过所有可用的建设工具和功能（最多至10级），逐步打造繁荣的零售帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras/1ae25d81089b55d09dd1cf875dc33154.avif?t=1746369392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras_big/1ae25d81089b55d09dd1cf875dc33154.avif?t=1746369392 width=800 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开拓你的领地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天都有新的挑战与机遇：谈判最佳交易、满足顾客需求，依靠毅力与智慧扩大你的品牌。成功不会从天而降，而是你一步步搭建而成的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用完整编辑器布局你的梦想商店</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从数十种货架中进行选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >订购产品，填满货架，设定有竞争力的价格吸引顾客</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性地摆放收银台以优化顾客流动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募、聘用并培训员工保持顾客满意度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展你的店铺，解锁新的布局，将小店变为超市</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计吸引顾客回访的购物体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚钱，壮大你的商店，击败竞争对手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由你制定规则！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras/4ce314be4ec7ed13fc399ab013d8c4b6.avif?t=1746369392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras_big/4ce314be4ec7ed13fc399ab013d8c4b6.avif?t=1746369392 width=800 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人畅玩，或者与最多3名朋友合作体验零售经营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展至10级：从小做起，梦想远大 – 扩建店铺，打造完美零售空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式管理：平衡库存、定价与顾客满意度，体验真实的商业经营。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不要仅止步于梦想，立即行动，打造你的帝国。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras/4796b5d9775bb6b88e32ada14926c116.avif?t=1746369392\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207060/extras_big/4796b5d9775bb6b88e32ada14926c116.avif?t=1746369392 width=800 height=187 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的商业帝国等待着你！</p>",
